forex_backtester/
│
├── data/
│   └── EURUSD_H1.csv  (You'll need to provide this data file)
│
├── backtester/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── engine.py        (The core backtesting logic)
│   ├── indicators.py    (Functions for technical indicators)
│   └── performance.py   (Functions for calculating metrics)
│   └── plotting.py      (Functions for visualization)
│
├── main.py              (The main script to run the backtest)
├── requirements.txt
└── README.md
